PN,44601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774451488
OL,3,CExecutive fail to agree minimum unit
OL,4,Calcohol pricing policy
OL,6,FMinimum unit alcohol pricing will not
OL,7,Fbe introduced in the current Assembly
OL,8,Fterm due to a failure to secure
OL,9,FExecutive agreement, Health Minister
OL,10,FMike Nesbitt has said.
OL,12,FMr Nesbitt told MLAs that the failure
OL,13,Fto introduce the policy was a missed
OL,14,Fopportunity which will have "an impact
OL,15,Fon many vulnerable and at-risk people
OL,16,Fin Northern Ireland".
OL,26,@vD@]OUxD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774451488
OL,3,CExecutive fail to agree minimum unit
OL,4,Calcohol pricing policy
OL,6,FBut DUP deputy First Minister Emma
OL,7,FLittle-Pengelly said her party had
OL,8,Fasked the Health Minister to "bring
OL,9,Fforward proposals that are based on
OL,10,Fevidence".
OL,12,FMr Nesbitt told the Northern Ireland
OL,13,FAssembly that he "regretted" having to
OL,14,Fmake the announcement.
OL,16,FHe said: "Minimum unit pricing or MUP
OL,17,Fhas been under discussion for a number
OL,18,Fof years and has been proposed by
OL,19,Fmultiple health ministers."
OL,26,@pD@^OUrD@IO]uD@ROUuD@\O]xD@JOU{D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774451488
OL,3,CExecutive fail to agree minimum unit
OL,4,Calcohol pricing policy
OL,6,FMr Nesbitt said MUP was "not a
OL,7,Fpanacea" but "would be an effective
OL,8,Fand targeted way" to address alcohol-
OL,9,Frelated harm.
OL,11,FHe added: "Primary legislation had
OL,12,Fbeen provisionally scheduled for
OL,13,Fintroduction in 2026-27.
OL,26,@nD@YOUoD@HO]oD@NOUpD@QO]sD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774451488
OL,3,CExecutive fail to agree minimum unit
OL,4,Calcohol pricing policy
OL,6,F"Unfortunately, however, despite my
OL,7,Fefforts to provide information and
OL,8,Faddress any concerns, it has not been
OL,9,Fpossible to secure Executive
OL,10,Fagreement, and we have now reached the
OL,11,Fpoint sadly where legislation for MUP
OL,12,Fis no longer deliverable in this
OL,13,Fmandate.
OL,15,F"This will have an impact on many
OL,16,Fvulnerable and at-risk people in
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOUyD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774451488
OL,3,CExecutive fail to agree minimum unit
OL,4,Calcohol pricing policy
OL,6,FThe minister said the British Heart
OL,7,FFoundation recently published a report
OL,8,Fwhich estimated that 676 people each
OL,9,Fyear in Northern Ireland die as a
OL,10,Fdirect result of their alcohol
OL,11,Fconsumption.
OL,13,FMr Nesbitt said evidence showed that
OL,14,FMUP would "reduce alcohol consumption,
OL,15,Fand lead to fewer people being
OL,16,Fadmitted to hospital and dying as a
OL,17,Fresult of their drinking".
OL,19,FHe added: "For example, in Scotland it
OL,20,Fis estimated that MUP has led to 120
OL,21,Ffewer alcohol deaths each year."
OL,26,@vD@KOUyD@YO]{D@KOU}D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774451488
OL,3,CExecutive fail to agree minimum unit
OL,4,Calcohol pricing policy
OL,6,FThe minister told the Assembly that
OL,7,Fmodelling had estimated that a 65p MUP
OL,8,Fwould lead to a reduction of 82
OL,9,Falcohol-related deaths a year in
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland and an annual
OL,11,Freduction of 3,482 alcohol-related
OL,12,Fhospital admissions.
OL,14,FHe said: "I have always been clear
OL,15,Fthat MUP is not a silver bullet, but
OL,16,Fis a proven, effective tool to reduce
OL,17,Falcohol harm."
OL,19,FMr Nesbitt told MLAs: "I feel that not
OL,20,Fintroducing MUP is a missed
OL,21,Fopportunity.
OL,26,@vD@JOUyD@NO]{D@WOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774451488
OL,3,CExecutive fail to agree minimum unit
OL,4,Calcohol pricing policy
OL,6,F"An opportunity which would have
OL,7,Fallowed this Assembly to make a
OL,8,Fmeaningful difference in reducing the
OL,9,Falcohol-related harms and inequalities
OL,10,Facross the region.
OL,12,F"I therefore reiterate my regret that
OL,13,FI am making this statement today,
OL,14,Frather than bringing forward
OL,15,Flegislation on setting an MUP.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774451488
OL,3,CExecutive fail to agree minimum unit
OL,4,Calcohol pricing policy
OL,6,F"While there is clearly insufficient
OL,7,Ftime left to legislate for MUP in this
OL,8,Fmandate, even if there was Executive
OL,9,Fagreement to do so, it would be my
OL,10,Ffervent hope that an incoming Health
OL,11,FMinister and Executive will be able to
OL,12,Fbring forward legislation early in the
OL,13,Fnext mandate to address this important
OL,14,Fpublic health issue."
OL,16,FSDLP health spokesperson Colin McGrath
OL,17,Faccused the DUP of blocking the policy.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774451488
OL,3,CExecutive fail to agree minimum unit
OL,4,Calcohol pricing policy
OL,6,FHe said: "It's unacceptable that when
OL,7,Fwe have majority Executive and
OL,8,FAssembly support for a vital public
OL,9,Fhealth intervention, one party is able
OL,10,Fto weaponise its veto and block it
OL,11,Ffrom being introduced.
OL,13,F"It was a DUP health minister who
OL,14,Ffirst floated this policy and they
OL,15,Fshould outline what has caused such a
OL,16,Fsharp change in tack.
OL,26,@nD@JOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774451488
OL,3,CExecutive fail to agree minimum unit
OL,4,Calcohol pricing policy
OL,6,F"We have a serious problem with
OL,7,Falcohol in our society, with hundreds
OL,8,Fof people dying each year and many
OL,9,Fmore affected by alcohol-related
OL,10,Fillness and harm, causing hospital
OL,11,Fadmissions and increased pressure on
OL,12,Four health service.
OL,14,F"This also has a really negative
OL,15,Fimpact on the lives of those affected
OL,16,Fby this illness and the people around
OL,17,Fthem."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUyD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774451488
OL,3,CExecutive fail to agree minimum unit
OL,4,Calcohol pricing policy
OL,6,FBut Ms Little-Pengelly said her party
OL,7,Fhad put questions to the health
OL,8,Fminister "to demonstrate that this
OL,9,Fintervention would actually work".
OL,11,FShe said: "Of course, we want to
OL,12,Freduce alcohol related deaths, this
OL,13,Fhits at a particular type of issue,
OL,14,Fbut the vast majority of alcohol for
OL,15,Fsale would not be impacted by this
OL,16,Fmeasure, and alcohol deaths hit on
OL,17,Fevery part of our society.
OL,19,F"Alcohol misuse is something that is a
OL,20,Fhuge burden for the health service.
OL,26,@pD@JOUqD@aO]sD@KOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774451488
OL,3,CExecutive fail to agree minimum unit
OL,4,Calcohol pricing policy
OL,6,F"We have asked the health minister to
OL,7,Fbring forward proposals that are based
OL,8,Fon evidence, that are based in
OL,9,Fsomething that will work, and we will
OL,10,Flook at that when that happens."
OL,12,FProfessor Sir Ian Gilmore, Chair of
OL,13,Fthe Alcohol Health Alliance, said the
OL,14,Fdecision is a "deeply disappointing
OL,15,Ffailure to act on a public health
OL,16,Fcrisis".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@`O]vD@OOUxD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774451488
OL,3,CExecutive fail to agree minimum unit
OL,4,Calcohol pricing policy
OL,6,FHe added: "The evidence is clear,
OL,7,Fminimum Unit Pricing is one of the
OL,8,Fmost effective and targeted measures
OL,9,Favailable to reduce alcohol-related
OL,10,Fdeaths, hospital admissions and health
OL,11,Finequalities, with the greatest
OL,12,Fbenefits felt among men and those
OL,13,Fliving in the most disadvantaged
OL,14,Fcommunities.
OL,16,F"Northern Ireland is facing its
OL,17,Fhighest levels of alcohol harm on
OL,18,Frecord, placing unacceptable burden on
OL,19,Findividuals, families, and public
OL,20,Fservices.
OL,26,@nD@KOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774451488
OL,3,CExecutive fail to agree minimum unit
OL,4,Calcohol pricing policy
OL,6,F"Choosing not to implement this policy
OL,7,Fmeans those harms will persist, with
OL,8,Fgrave consequences, and hitting the
OL,9,Fmost vulnerable groups in society the
OL,10,Fhardest."
OL,12,FHe added: "We urge policymakers to
OL,13,Freconsider this decision and to
OL,14,Fprioritise evidence-based measures
OL,15,Fthat protect public health over
OL,16,Fpolitical wins.
OL,18,F"Lives are being lost that could be
OL,19,Fsaved with this proven, preventative
OL,20,Fpolicy."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@IO]tD@KOUzD@AOU|D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/15
